<li>Scary Robot, cool</li>
<li>Human effigy, cooler</li>
<li>Crazy shit happens when it isn't well maintained, awesome</li>
<li>Potentially lethal scream, slightly cliche but still cool</li>
<li>Crazy shit includes….machines turning on. Neat, now what do they do?</li>
<li>Run.</li>
<li>So?</li>
<li>…that's it.</li>
</ul>
<p>See what I mean? You have a cool foundation but you don't quite build on it. At first I thought this was actually a giant automaton, and was expecting it to run around all giant or something, which would have admittedly been pretty cool (if a bit too Gundam-esque). Point is, you need to up the creep in some way. Withholding vote for now.</p>

